{"tid":2293823,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"秀智出道可愛斜邊短瀏海 韓網回憶殺：「當時覺得這髮型很好看！」","createTime":"2020-11-20T13:51:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T16:25:07.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"72ef4729dbaeeff6d66d3c4678a6b4bd43e0d030","tid":2293823,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T13:51:53.000Z","msg":"近期熱播韓劇《Start-Up》由秀智、南柱赫、金宣虎和姜漢娜主演，講述一群年輕人夢想在韓國「矽谷」成功創業並相互成長的故事。秀智在劇中的齊瀏海&amp;微卷長髮乃是許多粉絲心目中的女神造型，不過秀智也曾出現「顏值勝過一切」的髮型，到底是什麼造型引起韓網討論呢～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.presslogic.com/kdaily-image.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c01c6d6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.presslogic.com%2Fkdaily-image.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2Fc01c6d6a.jpg&h=9ae5b82b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://kdaily-image.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/850b8538.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkdaily-image.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F850b8538.gif&h=f805843d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.presslogic.com/kdaily-image.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8021aa2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.presslogic.com%2Fkdaily-image.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F8021aa2a.jpg&h=4d420055&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n秀智在2010年以女子團體Miss A出道，隔年便出演韓劇《夢想起飛Dream High》女主角，更是在2012年進軍電影圈演出《初戀築夢101》聲名大噪，成為所有韓國人心中的「國民初戀」！自此秀智接演了許多韓劇，演技變得更加純熟，而近日由於秀智主演的韓劇《Start-Up》正在跟播中，因此韓網有人就拿出秀智出道時的髮型，沒想到卻引起許多迴響～看來大家都是同年代的人，對這種髮型這麼有共鳴XD<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.presslogic.com/kdaily-image.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/cbdb46f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.presslogic.com%2Fkdaily-image.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2Fcbdb46f1.jpg&h=11792212&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46116da52535182f54c6c880db66cad698367338","tid":2293823,"uid":93096,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T13:52:22.000Z","msg":"最尾張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e770de67e36b266c8c8273c5169d24efd9690ea2","tid":2293823,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46116da52535182f54c6c880db66cad698367338","tid":2293823,"uid":93096,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T13:52:22.000Z","msg":"最尾張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T13:57:43.000Z","msg":"平的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84afa747bf33447b4339ff19d6e2e07e5f4f6592","tid":2293823,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:02:02.000Z","msg":"好復古<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37ff79c513a8844affac189cff0127797d545c9","tid":2293823,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:11:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有錢整鼻冇錢割雙眼皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b094e719102dda350185517afe7e1147244bdd07","tid":2293823,"uid":68678,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:40:40.000Z","msg":"宜家劣化得勁嚴重"},{"pid":"64d527f362545614508c51bfc8e636088c495342","tid":2293823,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"84afa747bf33447b4339ff19d6e2e07e5f4f6592","tid":2293823,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:02:02.000Z","msg":"好復古<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"